Elevation data: Schenectady

Load in packages

library(elevatr)
## Warning: package 'elevatr' was built under R version 4.0.5
library(AOI)

library(tmap)
## Warning: package 'tmap' was built under R version 4.0.3

Get bounding box coordinates for Union

loc2use <- aoi_get(x = list("Union College", 10,10) )
elevation <- get_elev_raster(loc2use, z = 14, clip = "bbox")
## Mosaicing & Projecting
## Clipping DEM to bbox
## Note: Elevation units are in meters.

Create in interactive map

tmap_mode("view")
## tmap mode set to interactive viewing
elevation %>% 
  tm_shape() +
  tm_raster(midpoint = NA, style = "cont") 
## stars object downsampled to 1149 by 871 cells. See tm_shape manual (argument raster.downsample)
## Linking to GEOS 3.8.0, GDAL 3.0.4, PROJ 6.3.1
elev_contours <- raster::rasterToContour(elevation)
tm_shape(elev_contours) +
  tm_iso()
## Warning in sp::proj4string(obj): CRS object has comment, which is lost in output
